---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 96
  - Title: Prajnâ-Pâramitâ (Diamond Sutra)
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Cosmic Dream
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Phantom Flux of Life
---
The phenomena of life may be likened unto a dream, a phantasm, a bubble, a
shadow, the glistening dew, or lightning flash, and thus they ought to be
contemplated.
